msg:
Server: 02c29c46-12b8-454f-9d25-66b59da5caff
QueryId: wg85128:7070
QueryEngine: CUBE[name=viw_bikyn_achis_trans_day_v3]
SQL: select viw_bikyn_dim_date.yy as viw_bikyn_dim_date_yy
		,viw_bikyn_dim_date.yy_desc as viw_bikyn_dim_date_yy_desc
		,viw_bikyn_dim_date.ss as viw_bikyn_dim_date_ss
		,viw_bikyn_dim_date.ss_desc as viw_bikyn_dim_date_ss_desc
		,viw_bikyn_dim_date.mon as viw_bikyn_dim_date_mon
		,viw_bikyn_dim_date.mon_desc as viw_bikyn_dim_date_mon_desc
		,viw_bikyn_dim_trans_chnl.trans_chnl as viw_bikyn_dim_trans_chnl_trans_chnl
		,viw_bikyn_dim_trans_chnl.trans_chnl_nm as viw_bikyn_dim_trans_chnl_trans_chnl_nm
		,viw_bikyn_dim_card_attr.card_attr as viw_bikyn_dim_card_attr_card_attr
		,viw_bikyn_dim_card_attr.card_attr_nm as viw_bikyn_dim_card_attr_card_attr_nm
		,viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2.mcc_grp_id3 as viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2_mcc_grp_id3
		,viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2.mcc_grp_desc3 as viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2_mcc_grp_desc3
		,viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2.mcc_grp_id2 as viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2_mcc_grp_id2
		,viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2.mcc_grp_desc2 as viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2_mcc_grp_desc2
		,sum(m.total_trans_num)*1.00 as total_trans_num
		,sum(m.achis_succ_trans_num)*1.00 as achis_succ_trans_num
from viw_bikyn_achis_trans_day m
left outer join viw_bikyn_dim_date as viw_bikyn_dim_date on m.hp_settle_dt = viw_bikyn_dim_date.dt
left outer join viw_bikyn_dim_trans_chnl as viw_bikyn_dim_trans_chnl on m.trans_chnl = viw_bikyn_dim_trans_chnl.trans_chnl
left outer join viw_bikyn_dim_card_attr as viw_bikyn_dim_card_attr on m.card_attr = viw_bikyn_dim_card_attr.card_attr
left outer join viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2 as viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2 on m.mcc = viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2.mcc_cd
where 1=1   
and (viw_bikyn_dim_trans_chnl.trans_chnl in ('0'))
and (viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2.mcc_grp_id3 in ('1'))
and (viw_bikyn_dim_card_attr.card_attr in ('01'))
and (viw_bikyn_dim_date.yy in ('2019'))
group by viw_bikyn_dim_date.yy
		,viw_bikyn_dim_date.yy_desc
		,viw_bikyn_dim_date.ss
		,viw_bikyn_dim_date.ss_desc
		,viw_bikyn_dim_date.mon
		,viw_bikyn_dim_date.mon_desc
		,viw_bikyn_dim_trans_chnl.trans_chnl
		,viw_bikyn_dim_trans_chnl.trans_chnl_nm
		,viw_bikyn_dim_card_attr.card_attr
		,viw_bikyn_dim_card_attr.card_attr_nm
		,viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2.mcc_grp_id3
		,viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2.mcc_grp_desc3
		,viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2.mcc_grp_id2
		,viw_bikyn_dim_mcc_new2.mcc_grp_desc2
